reviews.review_text: Days Between Thanx Scott.  Your efforts are greatly appreciated.  The quality is well described in the notes.  A slight distant feel to it, but everything is clear. I was at this show and have not heard it since.  Grateful to have it.  The Days Between is epic.  Well sung and a monster outro jam.  Black-throated is always nice and Samba is actually another 2nd set highlight.  I am opening my radio show this week with Drums thru Sugar Magnolia.  Peace
